CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, July 3, 1954, pg. 26, reads: "Top Performers - Shown above are some of the standout stars in annual Allegheny Mountain Association track and field meet held at Oliver Field last Saturday. In the photo on the left are David Peays and Arnie Sowell, Pitt runners who won individual honors in the meet... - Harris Photos."
TitMainTitle: University of Pittsburgh track stars David Peays holding medal, and Arnold "Arnie" Sowell, standing on Oliver Field, for annual Allegheny Mountain Association track and field championships
